Articles.Content:
REQUIRES TWEAKSCALE!!! Else it will NOT work, and it's an useful mod!

Overall View.

Top/Side View

Bottom/Silhouette.

-Fast, quite manouverable, very historical.

-Looks alot like the real F9F-6.

-Only F9F-6 I've managed to find.

Download here: http://www./download/bal5bahp09vh90c/Nieuw_-_WinRAR_ZIP-archief.zip

Open the file that contains the screenshots and the craft file, put the craft file in any save you like IN THE SPH folder, don't open the craft file as it will give you an error message. It will be put in the game's craft list, in that save.

Feel free to check out my F2H-2 Banshee http://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/threads/135962-F2H-2-Banshee-%28Tweakscale%29

GIVE ME YOUR SUGGESTIONS IN THE COMMENTS (please no props since I don't like making them). I'll pick the most-suggested plane for every post I make.

Have fun with it
